query:
insert into users(address, logo_nft, username, bio, twitter, instagram, facebook, link, email)
                values ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8, $9)
                on conflict (address)
                do update set logo_nft  = $2,
                              username  = $3,
                              bio       = $4,
                              twitter   = $5,
                              instagram = $6,
                              facebook  = $7,
                              link      = $8,
                              email     = $9
